{"tid":1904373,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次試 New Balance 籃球鞋 拍左條鞋評","createTime":"2020-02-29T14:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T02:20:23.000Z","uid":277406,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"09de5e6f6510985766476ea0b1acf24bca7238b6","tid":1904373,"uid":277406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:46:23.000Z","msg":"一路都見到外國好多鞋評片做得生動得黎又好專業 反觀香港少之有少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係香港人咁窮 啲野咁貴 買籃球鞋係好應該買對適合自己<br />\n唔通買完又後悔又整向左走向右走傷咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此 決定將自己買過既籃球鞋都拍鞋評比大家睇！<br />\n(只會介紹覺得好著既鞋)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s. 第一次係連登放自己既片 有咩講得唔好細力少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MPkhxShu_l4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMPkhxShu_l4&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=ea1bada2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MPkhxShu_l4</a>"},{"pid":"f853c3c85d9efa7412cb04cacb25ca96d943b107","tid":1904373,"uid":33875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"頭一分鐘飛咗，其他睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻鞋色好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beefb284e6892b9b75da6d407c8e46402f116bb4","tid":1904373,"uid":277406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f853c3c85d9efa7412cb04cacb25ca96d943b107","tid":1904373,"uid":33875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"頭一分鐘飛咗，其他睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\